measurements.description: One flower and one bud on one 29.5-cm sequentially blooming inflorescence; dorsal sepal white overlaid light green medially, heavily spotted burgundy, speckled marginally; synsepal white overlaid light green, light burgundy veins, burgundy spots proximal 2/3; petals light green overlaid burgundy except spotted burgundy proximally; pouch 30-degree angle from vertical, light green overlaid burgundy; staminode light green overlaid burgundy; substance medium; texture glossy.
